title: United States 10 Year TIPS Yield
description: 10 Year TIPS Yield was 1.64 percent on Tuesday November 8, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the United States 10 Year TIPS Yield reached an all time high of 4.41 in January of 2000. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United States 10 Year TIPS Yield.
author: Federal Reserve
